  "dateModified": "2026-03-29",
  "datePublished": "2026-03-29",
  "description": "The elimination of the temporal middle — the position of inheriting, continuing, and transforming — operates through the same structure as the physical genocide of Indigenous peoples. Physical, epistemic, linguistic, legal, and architectural elimination are the same operation at different scales.",
  "name": "The American Genocide Against the Temporal Middle",
